1. Imam tri *komada* hleba u korpi. (I have three *pieces* of bread in the basket.)
2. Molim vas, mogu li dobiti pet *komada* ove olovke? (Excuse me, can I have five *pieces* of this pencil?)
3. Proizvodimo 1000 *komada* automobila svake godine. (We produce 1000 *units* of cars every year.)
4. Želim da kupim 2 *komada* novih patika. (I want to buy 2 *pairs* of new sneakers.)
5. Ova torta se sastoji od mnogo *komada*. (This cake consists of many *pieces*.)
6. Podelićemo ih na *komade* kako bi svi dobili po malo. (We will divide them into *pieces* so that everyone gets a little bit.)
7. Da li ste videli *komad* papira negde ovde? (Have you seen a *piece* of paper somewhere around here?)
8. Tražim savet za  *komad* nameštaja koji bi se uklopio u moju dnevnu sobu. (I'm looking for advice on a *piece* of furniture that would fit in my living room.)
9. Od ovog materijala mogu napraviti 5 *komada* haljina. (I can make 5 *pieces* of dresses from this material.)
10. Uzeo sam *komad* mesa i stavio ga na roštilj. (I took a *piece* of meat and put it on the grill.)